.RH MOD.RECIPES-SOURCE PLAYDOUGH O "6 Feb 87" 1987
.RZ "PLAYDOUGH" "Homemade playdough"
I got this from a friend of mine.
It even
.I "smells"
like the real thing.
.IH "3 cups" "1 kg"
.IG "2 cups" "flour" "200 g"
.IG "1 cup" "salt" "250 g"
.IG "2 Tbsp" "cream of tartar" "20 g"
.IG "2 cups" "water" "5 dl"
.IG "1 Tbsp" "mineral oil" "15 ml"
.IG "" "food coloring"
.PH
.SK 1
Mix all ingredients in a saucepan.
Cook over medium heat, stirring until stiff.
.SK 2
Allow to cool; knead.
.SH RATING
.I Difficulty:
easy.
.I Time:
10 minutes.
.I Precision:
approximate measurement OK.
.WR
Jan Wolitzky
AT&T Bell Laboratories, Murray Hill, New Jersey, USA
